  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators' aim was to evaluate the population pharmacokinetics of montelukast in
      infants and children and define the appropriate dose in order to optimize Montelukast
      treatment in this vulnerable population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
